snippet: Matt Kenseth raced to victory in Richmond, Va., putting him in a tie with Kyle Busch and Jimmie Johnson for the top seeds in the Chase for the Sprint Cup
abstract: Results of final qualifying race for Chase for the Sprint Cup playoff series given; Matt Kenseth wins Richmond, Va, race, his fourth of the season.
lead_paragraph: Matt Kenseth raced to victory in Richmond, Va., putting him in a tie with Kyle Busch and Jimmie Johnson for the top seeds in the Chase for the Sprint Cup

headline.main: Matt Kenseth Is First in Race, and in Seeding
headline.print_headline: First in Race, and in Seeding
